revisions.description: The initial release of this management information module.

usdIpPolicyAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdIpPolicyAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the IP Policy component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdIpPolicyAgentV1.name: usdIpPolicyAgentV1
usdIpPolicyAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the IP Policy component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the IP Policy component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 1.x system releases.
usdIpPolicyAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Policy application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for the IP Named Access List.

usdIpPolicyAgentV2.name: usdIpPolicyAgentV2
usdIpPolicyAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the IP Policy component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the IP Policy component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 2.x system releases.
usdIpPolicyAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Policy application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for the IP ASP Access List, the IP Prefix List, the IP Prefix Tree, the IP Community List, the IP Extended Community List, IP Dynamic Route Redistribution, and the IP Route Map.

usdIpPolicyAgentV3.name: usdIpPolicyAgentV3
usdIpPolicyAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the IP Policy component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the IP Policy component is supported in the
        Unisphere RX 3.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdIpPolicyAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Policy application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
